With prefix ARG, prompt for a label type and include only labels of
that specific type."
  (interactive "P")
  (setq reftex-toc-include-labels 
	(if arg (reftex-query-label-type)
	  (not reftex-toc-include-labels)))
  (reftex-toc-revert))
